15:55.155 --> 15:56.723
- It's pro bono.

15:56.723 --> 15:59.392
Not all of us have to worry
about our next meal.

15:59.392 --> 16:01.028
- Getting personal,
that's promising.

16:01.028 --> 16:02.295
- Rita was just leaving.

16:02.295 --> 16:03.896
- I'll be right down
the block.

16:03.896 --> 16:06.066
- This won't take long.

16:06.066 --> 16:10.037
In about 20 minutes,
