16:12.205 --> 16:13.640
- This is serious.

16:13.640 --> 16:16.576
We got a DNA match.

16:16.576 --> 16:18.245
And you lied
about sexual contact.

16:18.245 --> 16:20.180
- I didn't--
- Let me answer, son.

16:20.180 --> 16:23.883
This is awkward, but it was the
