16:23.883 --> 16:27.087
He got excited and finished
before anything even started.

16:27.087 --> 16:28.655
- Not according
to Instagram.

16:28.655 --> 16:30.257
- He was trying
to impress his friends.

16:30.257 --> 16:31.858
- Then why did Abby
accuse you of rape?

16:31.858 --> 16:33.893
- How do you expect him
to explain that?

16:33.893 --> 16:35.328
- This girl
is obviously lying.

16:35.328 --> 16:37.097
- Why don't you
let Chris talk?

16:37.097 --> 16:38.498
- I'm here to speak for him.

16:38.498 --> 16:41.334
Chris was shocked
by these allegations.

16:41.334 --> 16:43.903
As far as he knew,
he and Abby were friends.

16:43.903 --> 16:47.107
- She still thinks we are.

16:47.107 --> 16:49.409
- Huh.
Help yourselves.

16:50.943 --> 16:52.512
- "I don't know
why this is happening.

16:52.512 --> 16:56.183
I like you.
I hope you're not mad at me."

16:56.183 --> 16:57.617
- See?
She's fine.

16:57.617 --> 16:59.086
- Oh, boy,
that's not good.

16:59.086 --> 17:00.287
Am I right, counselor?

17:00.287 --> 17:01.688
- Like a broken clock.

17:01.688 --> 17:04.857
- Okay, so she's
an imperfect victim.

17:04.857 --> 17:06.793
- Call your friend Calhoun.

17:06.793 --> 17:09.496
- My friend.

17:11.264 --> 17:12.865
- I never thought
I'd say this,

17:12.865 --> 17:14.367
but thank God
for texting.

17:14.367 --> 17:15.835
- [chuckles]
I'm tempted to send

17:15.835 --> 17:18.305
that girl's family
my legal bill.

17:20.273 --> 17:23.110
- So I assume
this will be the last

17:23.110 --> 17:24.611
we hear of the matter,
counselor?

17:24.611 --> 17:26.146
- We'll be in touch.

17:30.117 --> 17:31.718
Rita, we have a problem.

17:31.718 --> 17:33.453
- No, we don't.
I've already spoken with Abby,

17:33.453 --> 17:35.288
and this isn't anything
we haven't seen before.

17:35.288 --> 17:37.524
- Really? Because if you were
that boy's defense attorney,

17:37.524 --> 17:39.126
you'd tear her to shreds.

17:39.126 --> 17:40.627
- Put this into context.
Abby's insecure.

17:40.627 --> 17:42.329
She's non-confrontational.

17:42.329 --> 17:43.896
If she were more assertive,
we might not even be here.

17:43.896 --> 17:45.232
- She was assertive enough
to text him.

17:45.232 --> 17:47.734
- She was answering
his texts every time.

17:47.734 --> 17:49.736
There's no social protocol
with teenagers.

17:49.736 --> 17:51.538
Do you un-friend?
Do you block?

17:51.538 --> 17:52.972
They don't think
things through.

17:52.972 --> 17:54.141
- I understand,
but Buchanan's gonna

17:54.141 --> 17:55.575
crucify her
in front of a jury.

17:55.575 --> 17:58.545
- This boy lured Abby
into the school's darkroom,

17:58.545 --> 17:59.979
boasted on the internet
they had sex,

17:59.979 --> 18:01.281
lied to the police.

18:01.281 --> 18:02.882
- What do you want me to do?

18:02.882 --> 18:04.384
- There were a hundred kids
at that dance.

18:04.384 --> 18:07.620
Have you talked
to any of them?

18:07.620 --> 18:10.390
- Everyone knows the darkroom
is where you have sex.

18:10.390 --> 18:13.059
Once you go down there,
you can't change your mind.

18:13.059 --> 18:15.962
- Actually, you can,
Daniella, at any time.

18:15.962 --> 18:18.365
- Maybe, but there's
no way Abby did.

18:18.365 --> 18:20.367
She's obsessed with Chris.

18:20.367 --> 18:22.369
- So you think she's just
making this up?

18:22.369 --> 18:24.571
- I don't know.

18:24.571 --> 18:28.040
She could just be mad that Chris
didn't ask her out again.

18:30.009 --> 18:31.211
- [laughs]

18:31.211 --> 18:34.013
- Will Moore?
Jack Peters?

18:34.013 --> 18:35.014
- Yeah.

18:35.014 --> 18:37.049
- NYPD.
We got a couple questions.

18:37.049 --> 18:38.084
- About Chris?

18:38.084 --> 18:40.420
What people are saying
is unfair.

18:40.420 --> 18:43.223
He didn't do anything to Abby
she wasn't asking for.

18:43.223 --> 18:44.724
- She was asking for it?

18:44.724 --> 18:46.092
That's what you heard too?

18:46.092 --> 18:47.260
- Yeah, I guess.

18:47.260 --> 18:50.096
I got to go study, so...

18:52.932 --> 18:55.034
- Look, I don't want
to bad-mouth her,

18:55.034 --> 18:56.769
but Abby's just trying
to get attention.

18:56.769 --> 18:57.937
- Trying to avoid us, Jack?

18:57.937 --> 19:00.740
- No, I just
don't know anything.

19:00.740 --> 19:01.974
- What's the matter,

19:01.974 --> 19:03.976
