darkroom with her too?

19:03.976 --> 19:06.012
- You know, she's only 15.
You're 18.

19:06.012 --> 19:07.347
Know what that means?

19:07.347 --> 19:09.449
- Whoa, whoa, whoa,
I did not touch her.

19:09.449 --> 19:11.484
- Yeah, but Chris did though,
didn't he?

19:11.484 --> 19:15.121
Come on, talk to us or we're
gonna have to call your parents.

19:15.121 --> 19:17.123
- You know what, why don't
we just call Notre Dame?

19:17.123 --> 19:18.458
He's the one waiting to hear

19:18.458 --> 19:20.227
about that football
scholarship, right?

19:20.227 --> 19:23.230
- Wait, wait, wait, wait,
don't--don't do that.

19:23.230 --> 19:25.232
- Give us a reason not to.

19:28.034 --> 19:32.104
- Chris needed a name
on his list.

19:32.104 --> 19:35.375
- What list?

19:35.375 --> 19:39.045
- This secret society
for seniors.

19:39.045 --> 19:40.813
Nos Messis Cerasa.

19:40.813 --> 19:42.114
It's...

19:42.114 --> 19:44.951
It's Latin for
"Cherry Pickers Club."

19:47.153 --> 19:50.257
- What's the big secret?

19:50.257 --> 19:51.624
- It's this competition

19:51.624 --> 19:53.893
to see how many virgins
you can bang,

19:53.893 --> 19:58.164
and everybody had a name
on the list except for Chris.

20:00.867 --> 20:03.069
So, here, it's behind
this portrait.

20:12.879 --> 20:15.882
[dramatic music]

20:15.882 --> 20:20.553
