20:25.525 --> 20:27.059
but they came after me, okay?

20:27.059 --> 20:28.761
I could show you
the selfies they sent me.

20:28.761 --> 20:30.229
- That's okay.
We get it.

20:30.229 --> 20:32.265
- Chris only has
Abby listed?

20:32.265 --> 20:34.100
- Yeah, it's a good thing
he didn't get shut out,

20:34.100 --> 20:36.202
'cause that wall's there
forever.

20:41.708 --> 20:44.277
- Basically, Chris just
needed to make the wall.

20:44.277 --> 20:45.545
- Good to know.

20:45.545 --> 20:47.046
- Oh, counselor,
you're not gonna

20:47.046 --> 20:48.180
use this list though,
are you?

20:48.180 --> 20:49.316
- It goes to motive.

20:49.316 --> 20:50.817
- Yeah, but it also outs
a lot of teenagers.

20:50.817 --> 20:52.519
I mean, the guys, whatever.
Who cares about them?

20:52.519 --> 20:53.753
But these girls--

20:53.753 --> 20:55.522
- They don't want
this list going public.

20:55.522 --> 20:57.490
- Come on, like they haven't
posted darkroom selfies

20:57.490 --> 20:58.958
on their Facebook pages
already?

20:58.958 --> 21:00.993
We're dealing with
hormone-flooded teenagers.

21:00.993 --> 21:03.229
I know things are grey here,
but this is 50 shades of it.

21:03.229 --> 21:04.964
- I'm with Dodds.
I don't think this kid

21:04.964 --> 21:07.033
knew anything was wrong
till we showed up at his house.

21:07.033 --> 21:08.668
- He lied to your faces.

21:08.668 --> 21:10.036
- Yeah, and so did she

21:10.036 --> 21:12.972
when she said she wasn't
texting him anymore.

21:12.972 --> 21:15.808
- Okay, I think that
the kid is good for it,

21:15.808 --> 21:18.978
but going to trial
with where we are now...

21:18.978 --> 21:20.913
I think you need
to sit both families down

21:20.913 --> 21:22.382
and hammer out a plea.

21:22.382 --> 21:24.250
- I'll see what I can do.

21:26.152 --> 21:28.988
- A plea?

21:28.988 --> 21:30.923
Of misdemeanor
sexual misconduct?

21:30.923 --> 21:32.859
No.

21:32.859 --> 21:34.827
- I can't offer felony rape
or even attempted rape.

21:34.827 --> 21:36.363
A public defender
would balk at that.

21:36.363 --> 21:37.764
- There are other felonies.

21:37.764 --> 21:39.566
What about sending
indecent material

21:39.566 --> 21:41.033
to a minor via the texts.

21:41.033 --> 21:42.502
- The texts are pathetic,

21:42.502 --> 21:44.170
but I'm not sure
that they're indecent.

21:44.170 --> 21:46.739
Sexual misconduct does get him
on the sex offenders registry.

21:46.739 --> 21:48.375
Even if he doesn't
do jail time,

21:48.375 --> 21:50.242
his DNA goes into
the database,

21:50.242 --> 21:52.379
and being on the registry
is quite severe.

21:52.379 --> 21:54.681
- As it should be.
- No.

21:54.681 --> 21:57.083
He raped my daughter.
He should go to prison!

21:57.083 --> 21:58.551
- We're all upset
about what happened to Abby,

21:58.551 --> 22:00.286
but putting her
through a trial?

22:00.286 --> 22:03.022
There's a good chance that
does not result in a conviction.

22:03.022 --> 22:04.123
Counselor?

22:04.123 --> 22:05.658
- Mr. Barba
is making good points.

22:05.658 --> 22:07.627
Even with the rape shield law,

22:07.627 --> 22:10.196
the press will be all over
this story if we go forward.

22:10.196 --> 22:13.099
- The press?
My life is over.

22:13.099 --> 22:15.034
Everybody at school
is whispering about me,

22:15.034 --> 22:16.035
laughing at me.

22:16.035 --> 22:17.404
- Abby, honey, please--

22:17.404 --> 22:19.038
- Chris' friends hate me.

22:19.038 --> 22:22.074
My friends hate me.
I wish I'd never said anything.

22:28.981 --> 22:30.917
- I'm sorry.

22:33.119 --> 22:35.087
This is all I can do.

22:37.557 --> 22:39.826
- We'll take
sexual misconduct.

22:39.826 --> 22:44.431
As long as Chris Roberts
goes on the registry.

22:46.499 --> 22:48.234
- The registry?
Absolutely not.

22:48.234 --> 22:49.502
- This is the best plea
I can offer.

22:49.502 --> 22:50.970
Your son would avoid

22:50.970 --> 22:52.672
the publicity and trauma
of a trial.

22:52.672 --> 22:55.141
- But he'd be put on a list
with rapists and pedophiles.

22:55.141 --> 22:56.476
What about college?

22:56.476 --> 22:58.144
- Chris just got
early acceptance to Stanford.

22:58.144 --> 22:59.579
- That's nice.

22:59.579 --> 23:01.881
- If he goes on the list,
he can't have a smartphone.

23:01.881 --> 23:03.450
He can't even access
the internet.

23:03.450 --> 23:05.117
To make this go away,

23:05.117 --> 23:08.054
we'd consider endangering
the welfare of a child.

23:08.054 --> 23:10.089
- He had unwanted sexual
contact with a minor.

23:10.089 --> 23:13.460
He has to go
on the registry.

23:13.460 --> 23:15.762
- Did Benson and Calhoun
prepare that sentence for you?

23:15.762 --> 23:17.630
We all know
what this was.

23:17.630 --> 23:19.298
A misunderstanding

23:19.298 --> 23:21.768
between two sexually
inexperienced teenagers.

23:21.768 --> 23:23.169
- One of whom
is 15 years old.

23:23.169 --> 23:24.671
That's automatic
sexual misconduct.

23:24.671 --> 23:25.838
- That's your best argument?

23:25.838 --> 23:27.474
There's a Romeo
and Juliet exemption.

23:27.474 --> 23:28.675
- Not if he forced her.

23:28.675 --> 23:30.610
- That's her story,
after the fact.

23:30.610 --> 23:31.978
- This train is leaving
the station.

23:31.978 --> 23:33.345
I've offered you
no prison time.

23:33.345 --> 23:35.081
If you say no
and your son is convicted,

23:35.081 --> 23:36.916
prison time is what
he could be looking at.

23:36.916 --> 23:38.184
- But he didn't do
anything wrong.

23:38.184 --> 23:40.086
- Chris,
is this what you want?

23:40.086 --> 23:41.153
To go to trial?

23:41.153 --> 23:42.822
- Does that mean
I'm on the news?

23:42.822 --> 23:44.156
Everybody knows
who I am?

23:44.156 --> 23:45.825
- Once you're arrested
and charged,

23:45.825 --> 23:47.594
your name is made public.

23:47.594 --> 23:50.362
Anytime anyone Googles you
for the rest of your life,

23:50.362 --> 23:52.331
this is what will come up.

23:52.331 --> 23:54.000
- Don't threaten my son.

23:54.000 --> 23:55.267
This girl's slandering him.

23:55.267 --> 23:57.303
We need to fight this.

23:57.303 --> 24:00.339
- Mr. Barba, what if I just say
sorry to Abby and her family?

24:00.339 --> 24:02.174
- You have nothing
to be sorry for.

24:02.174 --> 24:04.276
- No, absolutely not.
Let's go.

24:05.878 --> 24:07.346
- We're calling your bluff.

24:07.346 --> 24:09.215
No deal.

24:22.261 --> 24:22.895
- Chris Roberts,
you are charged

24:24.396 --> 24:25.765
