of attempted rape

24:25.765 --> 24:27.399
and two counts
of sexual misconduct

24:27.399 --> 24:29.101
and forcible touching.

24:29.101 --> 24:30.436
How do you plead?

24:30.436 --> 24:32.304
- Not guilty on all counts,
Your Honor.

24:32.304 --> 24:33.773
- People on bail?

24:33.773 --> 24:35.642
- The defendant has a passport
and the means to flee.

24:35.642 --> 24:37.109
We request 1 million.

24:37.109 --> 24:39.311
- For an 18-year-old
high school honors student

24:39.311 --> 24:40.713
with no priors
who lives at home?

24:40.713 --> 24:43.550
In lieu of bail,
we ask that he be released

24:43.550 --> 24:45.151
into his parents' custody.

24:45.151 --> 24:46.385
- I'll split the difference.

24:46.385 --> 24:48.120
Bail is set at 500,000.

24:48.120 --> 24:50.122
The defendant will
surrender his passport.

24:53.726 --> 24:55.227
- Lieutenant.

24:55.227 --> 24:57.229
- Dodds, glad you made it.

24:57.229 --> 24:59.131
You know, it's helpful
for the victims

24:59.131 --> 25:00.132
to see us in the gallery.

25:00.132 --> 25:01.568
- Yeah, about this victim,

25:01.568 --> 25:03.970
I'm sorry I brought it up
in front of everybody.

25:03.970 --> 25:05.371
- Don't be.
It's not a problem.

25:05.371 --> 25:06.639
- It's just that
these two teenagers

25:06.639 --> 25:08.107
both seem like good kids.

25:08.107 --> 25:10.577
I don't think they know
what happened in that darkroom.

25:10.577 --> 25:11.844
Do we?

25:11.844 --> 25:13.312
- Look, he may not realize

25:13.312 --> 25:15.481
that what he did
was a sexual assault,

25:15.481 --> 25:16.983
but Abby didn't make this up.

25:16.983 --> 25:19.485
She's just not
a manipulative girl.

25:19.485 --> 25:21.420
- Yeah, okay,
but he's not a predator.

25:21.420 --> 25:23.422
This is a high school
make out session gone bad.

25:23.422 --> 25:24.591
They shouldn't be going
to trial.

25:24.591 --> 25:26.192
- I don't disagree
with you.

25:26.192 --> 25:27.259
Not our call.

25:27.259 --> 25:28.394
- It wasn't theirs either.

25:28.394 --> 25:30.029
This whole thing
is a runaway train.

25:30.029 --> 25:32.599
- Good morning.

25:35.434 --> 25:38.605
- Wow, they made Chris
look like Harry Potter.

25:38.605 --> 25:40.607
- Well, we've seen
that before, right?

25:40.607 --> 25:42.775
The nerd defense.

25:46.679 --> 25:49.015
- The night Abby came home
after being assaulted,

25:49.015 --> 25:50.617
the defendant texted her.

25:50.617 --> 25:52.619
"I had a great time tonight.
See you Monday."

25:52.619 --> 25:54.120
She wrote back, "K."

25:54.120 --> 25:58.224
A week later, while Mr. Roberts
was being interrogated by SVU,

25:58.224 --> 25:59.626
she texted him again.

25:59.626 --> 26:01.661
"I don't know why
this is happening.

26:01.661 --> 26:04.496
I like you.
I hope you're not mad at me."

26:04.496 --> 26:07.299
In your years
as an SVU detective,

26:07.299 --> 26:09.101
sergeant, and now lieutenant,

26:09.101 --> 26:11.270
have you ever seen
this kind of communication

26:11.270 --> 26:12.672
between a young victim
and an assailant?

26:12.672 --> 26:14.707
- Yes, it's more common
than not.

26:14.707 --> 26:17.443
Look, teenagers have
imperfect judgment.

26:17.443 --> 26:20.847
I mean, in my experience,
a young, naive girl

26:20.847 --> 26:23.683
who also attends the same
high school as her rapist

26:23.683 --> 26:26.285
would be scared
of causing conflict

26:26.285 --> 26:28.788
or, worse, being stigmatized
by her peers.

26:28.788 --> 26:30.389
- In your experience,
this would be true

26:30.389 --> 26:31.991
of someone like Abby?

26:31.991 --> 26:33.993
- Yes, girls like Abby
who are shy

26:33.993 --> 26:36.729
have trouble speaking up
for themselves,

26:36.729 --> 26:41.333
and teenaged predators often
prey on less-assertive victims.

26:41.333 --> 26:43.569
- Okay, so one last question.

26:43.569 --> 26:48.074
Abby didn't file a report

26:48.074 --> 26:50.710
with the police
immediately afterwards.

26:50.710 --> 26:52.378
How unusual is that?

26:52.378 --> 26:54.380
- Oh, it's not unusual.
At all.

26:54.380 --> 26:56.382
It happens with many,
many victims.

26:56.382 --> 26:57.984
- Thank you, Lieutenant.

26:57.984 --> 26:59.752
- Good morning, Lieutenant.

26:59.752 --> 27:01.220
If I understood you
just now,

27:01.220 --> 27:04.090
it's because the assailant
is naive or shy

27:04.090 --> 27:07.426
that she waited four days
to disclose?

27:07.426 --> 27:08.761
- No, that's not
what I said.

27:08.761 --> 27:10.897
I said it's not unusual at all

27:10.897 --> 27:13.700
for any victim
to wait to disclose.

27:13.700 --> 27:17.303
