The problem is
is that teenage boys

40:39.237 --> 40:41.072
even in college
don't know what behavior

40:41.072 --> 40:43.008
might constitute rape.

40:43.008 --> 40:45.010
We need to make
the lines clearer.

40:45.010 --> 40:46.411
