41:35.561 --> 41:36.962
- Now you're sorry?

41:36.962 --> 41:38.196
- Don't you apologize
to him, sweetie.

41:38.196 --> 41:39.464
- Now is not the time.

41:39.464 --> 41:40.732
- Abby, you have nothing
to apologize for.

41:40.732 --> 41:42.067
- You can't tell me
that she didn't know

41:42.067 --> 41:44.369
