when she went into that room.

41:44.369 --> 41:46.404
- You all can lie to yourselves
all you want!

41:46.404 --> 41:48.206
We know exactly
what your son is!

41:48.206 --> 41:50.208
And now he's on the registry,
and everyone will know!

41:50.208 --> 41:52.578
- We know what your daughter is!
